quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,52,"Tuma Й“e naatunoo ka makko Й“e mbi'i: "Salaam (Kisiyee mon)". O maaki: "minen ko min Й—enЖґii Й“e on"."
  15,53,"ЖЃe mbi'i: "Wota a faay, minen miЙ—en mbeltinirma [Й“iЙ—Й—o] gorko ganndo"."
  15,54,"O maaki: "E on mbeltiniratkam [Й—uum] e hoore ko mi naywi ko? E ko mbeltinirton mi?""
  15,55,"ЖЃe mbi'i: "min mbeltininirii ma goonga, wota a jeye e taЖґiiЙ“e Й“een"."
  15,56,"O maaki: "Ko hommbo taЖґotoo e yurmeende Joomi mun nden, si wonaa majjuЙ“e Й“een?""
  15,57,"O maaki: "Ko woni fii mon, onon Й“ee imminaaЙ“e?"(nuleeЙ“e.)"
  15,58,"ЖЃe mbi'i: "minen min nulaa ko e yimЙ“e bonЙ“e,"
  15,59,"si wonaa Й“eynguure Luuti nde, pellet ko min daЙ—ndooЙ“e Й“e denndaangal,"
  15,60,"si wonaa debbo makko on". min koddirii oon Й—on ko jeyaaЙ—o e halketeeЙ“e Й“en."
  15,61,"Nde imminaaЙ“e Й“en ngaruno ka Й“eynguure Luuti,"
  15,62,"O maaki: "onon ko on yimЙ“e faaytaa Й“e"."
  15,63,"ЖЃe mbi'i: "Wurin min ngaddanii ma ko Й“e ngonnoo e sikkitaade kon."
  15,64,"Min ngaddanii ma goonga kan, pellet ko min goonЕ‹Й—uЙ“e."
  15,65,"Yahdu e Й“eynguure maa ndeen ka taЖґitannde jem- ma, jokkaa Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e; hara gooto e mo'on yeЖґЖґitaaki, ndewon ka njamiraЙ—on"."
  15,66,"Min anndini mo on fiyaaku: wonnВґde wattannde Й“ee Й—oo, ko taЖґeteeЙ—um ka subaka."
  15,67,"YimЙ“e saare nden ngri heЙ“e mbeltoro."
  15,68,"O maaki: "Й“ee Й—oo ko hoЙ“Й“e am, wata on wirtam.(cuhritam)."
  15,69,"Kulee Alla, wota on koynam"."
  15,70,"ЖЃe mbi'i: "e min kaЙ—aali ma [weernugol] tagoore nden?""